VERSIONTOKEN_EXTRA_INFO: Shows the players collection of Version Tokens. Using this command without a prompt will show your Version Token collection, adding another player's username or user id will show their Version Token collection if public, which can then be sorted and filtered in various ways. Using this command with additional prompts will show the collection with the specific filter already applied to it. Use the prompt "t:ut" in addition to this command to highlight all Version Tokens in your collection that currently don't have a tag. Use the "{{prefix}}help filter" command to see all available filters
